data.text:
Looking to travel from Lewes to Newhaven Harbour by train? You've come to the right place!

On average, it takes around 12 minutes to travel from Lewes to Newhaven Harbour by train, the fastest services can get you there in as little as 11 minutes though. You'll usually find 28 trains per day running along the 6 miles (9 km) route between these two destinations. Once you're onboard, you can sit back and relax, as you won't need to make any changes on your way to Newhaven Harbour. Southern are the main train operator on this route and will whisk you to Newhaven Harbour in no time.

To help you get great train deals, we'll highlight the cheapest train ticket prices from Lewes to Newhaven Harbour in our Journey Planner. Just remember, as well as travelling Off-Peak or using a Railcard, the sooner you book your tickets, the more you'll save, as advance tickets start from €4.29.
